            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "高盛下調中國經濟增長率至4.7%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">高盛預計，中國今年只會減息一次，幅度為10個基點，此前預期為兩次；因應美伊衝突至油價上升，更新了對亞洲經濟體的增長預測。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該行把中國今年實際GDP增長預期，從4.8%下調至4.7%；居民消費價格指數(CPI)預測則上調至0.9%，該機構日前已將這一預期從0.6%調升至0.8%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">高盛報告認為，亞洲貨幣政策預測基本保持不變，將大多數亞洲經濟體的增長預期下調0.3至0.5個百分點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15738016-%e9%ab%98%e7%9b%9b%e4%b8%8b%e8%aa%bf%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b7%e7%8e%87%e8%87%b34-7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20240305_FI_source-ap_china-economy_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 16:11:11",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "摩根大通租用新地西九藝術廣場大樓25萬呎樓面 租期10年",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新鴻基地產（新地）宣布，投資銀行摩根大通（J.P. Morgan）將成為西九文化區「藝術廣場大樓」（Artist Square Towers，簡稱AST）的首席租戶，其已承諾租用AST東西兩座大樓相連的六層樓面，總面積約25萬平方呎，租約為期10年。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"摩根大通租用新地西九藝術廣場大樓25萬呎樓面。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/700x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/WhatsApp-Image-2026-03-13-at-14.50.14.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"摩根大通租用新地西九藝術廣場大樓25萬呎樓面。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/700x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/WhatsApp-Image-2026-03-13-at-14.50.14.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">摩根大通租用新地西九藝術廣場大樓25萬呎樓面。</p>\n</a>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：摩根大通官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250522_FI_source-web_JPMorgan_Logo_Hong_Kong.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：摩根大通官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250522_FI_source-web_JPMorgan_Logo_Hong_Kong.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：摩根大通官網</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
